You don't like him in the show.

301
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,560
You like him off set.

302
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,240
Zhang Zhun.

303
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,600
Why are your eyes swollen?

304
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:12,120
And bloodshot!

305
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:13,560
Didn't sleep well last night?

306
00:18:14,306 --> 00:18:15,306
Last night,

307
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,960
there were mosquitoes in my room.

308
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,000
They kept me awake.

309
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:20,600
Mr. Zhang, try this.

310
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,040
It clears redness.

311
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:23,440
Don't let it affect filming.

312
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,160
Mr. Zhang.

313
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:26,360
Let me.

314
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:29,120
Relax.

315
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:30,680
I'm great with eye drops.

316
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,120
Thanks, then.

317
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:37,280
Come on.

318
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:50,000
Mr. Zhang looks so pitiful in tears.

319
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,320
You must be good at crying.

320
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,400
Departments ready.

321
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,120
Three.
Two.
One.

322
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,160
Action.

323
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:11,600
What did you think about
after you went home?

324
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,280
You.

325
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,760
Can you handle this distance?

326
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,720
Mm.

327
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:35,840
What about this?

328
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,920
This...

329
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:40,960
Feels strange.

330
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,320
Now,

331
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:44,920
let's try touching.

332
00:19:58,920 --> 00:19:59,920
Can we stop?

333
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,040
Try to endure it a little longer.

334
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:06,760
Cut.

335
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,880
No, no.

336
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:09,920
That's all wrong.

337
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,400
What's wrong, Director?

338
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:12,680
Zhen Xin.

339
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,200
At this point,

340
00:20:14,360 --> 00:20:15,120
you and Zhang Zhun

341
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:16,400
aren't there yet.

342
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,440
Do you understand?

343
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,200
Zhang Zhun.
Oh.

344
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:19,280
Wrong name.
Gao Zhun.

345
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:20,840
Gao Zhun.

346
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:23,480
I thought this would add tension.

347
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,400
If we follow that logic,

348
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:27,360
every dialogue scene needs a closed set.

349
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:28,160
No.

350
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:29,920
That's not the mood I want.

351
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:31,080
Adjust it now.

352
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,320
Honey.

353
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,520
Have some water.

354
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:37,560
Take a break.

355
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:39,360
We barely started.

356
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,040
Mr. Zhang.

357
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:44,520
Thanks for working with our Zhen Xin.

358
00:20:45,320 --> 00:20:45,680
How about this?

359
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,520
Dinner is on me tonight.

360
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:48,720
Hot pot?

361
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:49,880
Don't make random plans.

362
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:51,640
The crew is busy.

363
00:20:52,120 --> 00:20:53,480
Who has the time or energy?

364
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,880
I'll go.

365
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:55,560
Sounds good.

366
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:56,720
I'll arrange it.

367
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,480
Where are you from, Mr. Zhang?

368
00:21:17,160 --> 00:21:17,920
Sichuan.

369
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:18,960
I like spicy food.

370
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,720
Too bad.

371
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:22,520
Mr. Zhen and I

372
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:23,800
don't usually eat spicy food.

373
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,160
His stomach is weak.

374
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:29,359
How long...
have you two been together?

375
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:30,520
Us?

376
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,080
Almost a year, I guess.

377
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:33,680
Not that long.

378
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:35,040
We're both busy.

379
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,360
We may not meet once a month.

380
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:39,520
But even so,

381
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:41,600
we're still together.

382
00:21:42,360 --> 00:21:44,160
Isn't that true love, Honey?

383
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:49,280
Mr. Zhang.

384
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,720
What about you?

385
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:52,720
I...

386
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:55,080
I'm getting married soon.

387
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:58,960
After this show.

388
00:22:12,360 --> 00:22:13,360
I'm eating.

389
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:15,720
Mm.
I'm free.

390
00:22:16,800 --> 00:22:17,800
Go ahead.

391
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,240
Yesterday,

392
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,600
why were you holding his hand?

393
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:32,760
If I hadn't shown up,

394
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,040
what were you going to do?

395
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:43,000
This hot pot

396
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,480
has two separate broths.

397
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:47,240
I don't care what you do with yours.

398
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:50,200
But don't touch mine.

399
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,760
Besides,

400
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,640
what even is that broth?

401
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:03,640
Why aren't you eating?

402
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:05,040
I was waiting for you.

403
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,200
This is cooked.

404
00:23:07,360 --> 00:23:08,360
Try it.

405
00:23:21,360 --> 00:23:22,360
Honey.

406
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:24,680
Eating it that spicy

407
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:26,040
is bad for your stomach.

408
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,000
It's my stomach.

409
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:30,080
I'll do what I want.

410
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:48,040
Enjoy your meal.

411
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:51,280
I have something to do.

412
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:18,920
Who the fuck are you calling?

413
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:20,520
Chase me if you dare.

414
00:24:21,840 --> 00:24:22,840
It's me.

415
00:24:28,760 --> 00:24:29,760
I'm sorry.

416
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:31,240
I'm sorry.

417
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,480
Danyi.

418
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:34,760
I...

419
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,240
Are you okay?

420
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,640
I'm fine.

421
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,480
Are you

422
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,280
alone?

423
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,160
I was with

424
00:24:57,600 --> 00:24:58,600
a friend.

425
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,760
With a friend.

426
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:05,800
And

427
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:12,360
his girlfriend.

428
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:16,720
Are you coming back?

429
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:21,080
When all this is over,

430
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:22,880
will you come back?

431
00:25:29,360 --> 00:25:30,360
I...

432
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,160
Danyi.

433
00:25:38,320 --> 00:25:39,320
I don't know.

434
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:41,040
I can wait.

435
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:42,760
I mean,

436
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:44,560
if you come back,

437
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:46,040
I'll wait at home.

438
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:07,760
I'm sorry.

439
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,280
Please give me more time.

440
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:19,400
I need to find the answer.

441
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:30,960
I came after you.

442
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:34,600
Zhang Zhun.

443
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:24,640
Four hundred seventy-two steps.

444
00:27:28,080 --> 00:27:29,360
After leaving the hot pot place,

445
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:34,080
you walked 472 steps.

446
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:40,120
You took the call.

447
00:27:41,280 --> 00:27:42,760
I followed behind you.

448
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:51,520
Like a stray dog.

449
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:24,520
Why are you...

450
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:26,960
crying?

451
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:47,360
I'll break up with her.

452
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:58,840
Me too.

453
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:33,840
Know what Chen Zhengsen said about us?

454
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,480
He said

455
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:47,240
we're doomed.

456
00:30:15,840 --> 00:30:17,960
Xie Danyi.

457
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:41,120
Stop chasing.

458
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:49,320
What if you catch him?

459
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,040
There's a bar nearby.

460
00:31:00,840 --> 00:31:01,840
Have a drink.

461
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,440
I don't know you.

462
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,440
Now you do.

463
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:29,960
Don't worry.

464
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,240
There are cameras here.

465
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,640
It's safe.

466
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:34,880
I'm Feng Yunting.

467
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,440
Zhen Xin's girlfriend.

468
00:31:42,840 --> 00:31:44,080
I never drink.

469
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:00,200
Then why did you

470
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:01,520
stop me just now?

471
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,160
Did you really want

472
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,520
to chase him

473
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,240
and lose even harder?

474
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,280
Be kinder to yourself.

475
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,280
In this world,

476
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,720
plenty of things

477
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,400
are worth living for.

478
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:18,680
Men are not one of them.

479
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:21,640
If you keep giving in,

480
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:23,360
in the end,

481
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,400
only you get hurt.

482
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:28,680
Enjoy.
Thank you.

483
00:32:30,120 --> 00:32:31,120
This one's alcohol-free.

484
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:32,920
Drink slowly.

485
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:37,280
But are you okay giving up?

486
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,480
Silly.

487
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:42,120
It's like this drink.

488
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,560
I've already paid for it.

489
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:48,360
I can force myself to finish it.

490
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:50,840
Or throw it in someone's face.

491
00:32:52,080 --> 00:32:53,600
What I choose

492
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,520
depends on what makes me happy.

493
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:58,480
Or

494
00:32:58,720 --> 00:32:59,800
what makes me better.

495
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:07,560
Silly.

496
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,760
Losing love isn't shameful.

497
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,840
Losing yourself

498
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,680
is the ugly part.

499
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:17,880
Take your time.

500
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:23,280
I'm off.

501
00:33:57,800 --> 00:33:58,880
I'll handle it.

502
00:34:03,360 --> 00:34:03,800
Oh my God.

503
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:05,080
I can't with you two.

504
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:06,480
Reporters are waiting outside.

505
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,680
And you still...

506
00:34:09,600 --> 00:34:10,560
They're all watching you.

507
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:11,600
How dare you do this?

508
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:13,760
You two hide.

509
00:34:17,160 --> 00:34:17,640
Everyone.

510
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:19,160
This is the crew hotel.

511
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:20,160
Please don't...
Mr. Zhen.

512
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,536
You and Miss Feng Yunting
have dated for six months.

513
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:24,200
Why go public now?

514
00:38:05,953 --> 00:38:06,913
[He's asking AI]

515
00:38:07,066 --> 00:38:09,480
If you dream about someone.

516
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,880
And the dreams are all intimate,

517
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:13,600
what does that mean?

518
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:18,800
It means your subconsciousis expressing
unmet intimacy and sexual needs.

519
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:22,040
That person also represents
traits you desire.

520
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,080
Does that mean.

521
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,160
I like him?

522
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:46,040
If the intimacy in your dream leaves
you happy when you wake,

523
00:38:46,080 --> 00:38:47,240
wanting to get closer,

524
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:49,600
and caring about
everything they do in real life,

525
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:52,480
then it's likely yoursubconscious speaking.

526
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:53,520
You like them.

527
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,080
Why not sit in the second row?

528
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:19,040
Do you know why
Laozi wrote the Tao Te Ching?

529
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:22,960
Because I/he wanted
to. [A really bad pun]
